          <li>Medication prompting</li>
          <li>Domestic tasks such as laundry, ironing and cleaning</li>
          <li>Bathing</li>
          <li>Assistance with evening care routine</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To discuss your requirements, please <a href="contact.html">contact us</a> or call us on <a href="tel:01344876099" class="tel">01344 876099</a>. If you wish to go ahead, we will then arrange an appointment for you, normally with our Care Manager Olivia Macleay, to construct a suitable Care Plan.</p>
